name: Fauna Flowers 03 - Mico Flower
description:
Look up to admire this cheerful, playful and trickster flower. It prefers height than ground and usually grows on top of the trees. It loves to feel the wind and swing on the branches. A symbol of resilience of our biodiversity.

Fauna Flowers is a collection made of animals mixed with plants in a new kind of magical possibilities. Discover this world where flowers can be a magnificent diversity of beautiful and unique creatures.
